OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FScotland's health secretary
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25Fquits over iPad row        
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5F                           
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Scotland's health secretary Michael    
OL,6, Matheson, whose sons racked up an      
OL,7, #11,000 bill on his parliamentary iPad 
OL,8, while on holiday, has resigned.        
OL,10,FMr Matheson said he was standing down  
OL,11,Fbecause he did not want the row over   
OL,12,Fthe bill to become a distraction.      
OL,14,FIt comes ahead of the publication of an
OL,15,Finvestigation into the incident by the 
OL,16,FScottish Parliament Corporate Body.    
OL,18,FThe iPad charges, initially paid out of
OL,19,Fthe public purse, were incurred during 
OL,20,Fa trip to Morocco in late 2022.        
